   VERSION=( "2_1" "2_0" )
  CATEGORY="font"
 ATTRIBUTE="library"
    SOURCE="fcpackage.$VERSION"
       URL="http://fontconfig.org/release"
  HOMEPAGE="http://fontconfig.org"
 CONFLICTS="Xft"
       REQ="fontconfig"
     SHORT="Xft2 provides a client-side font API for X applications."
cat << EOF
About Xft

The current version of Xft (2.0) provides 
a client-side font API for X applications.
It uses Fontconfig to select fonts 
and the X protocol for rendering them.
When available, Xft uses the Render
extension to accelerate text drawing.
When Render is not available, Xft uses the 
core protocol to draw client-side glyphs.
This provides completely compatible support 
of client-side fonts for all X servers.
EOF
